"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-ellen-van-dijk-confirmed-for-paris-olympics-six-weeks-after-fracturing-ankle\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Dutch rider makes stunning recovery in time to start time trial and road race  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999979078733361, \"rank\": 2.0912025828510634e-06, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  Six weeks after fracturing her ankle,Ellen van Dijkhas won therace against timeto recover and will race in the 2024 Paris Olympics time trial and road race for the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\", \"score\": 0.9999998107509961, \"rank\": 1.491612308790252e-07, \"text\": \"Ellen\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\"}, {\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999994986161602, \"rank\": 5.013841928858444e-07, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Dijksustained the injury during a training camp in Spainat the start of June, before undergoing surgery and completing training adapted for the cast on her right leg to rebuild her race fitness.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheDutch Cycling Federation (KNWU) announced Van Dijk's participationon Wednesday, 10 days before the individual time trial, after \\\"variousperformancetests showed that she is ready to represent the Netherlands with ambition\\\".\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999592859256333, \"rank\": 4.07157088002051e-05, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.033135118183959e-34, \"text\": \"KNWU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999994986161602, \"rank\": 5.013841928858444e-07, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never Give Up!\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my mantra for over 6 weeks now.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step I kept repeating it to myself.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not give up, it is still possible.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I took it day by day, although it wasn't easy,\\\" said Van Dijk onInstagramafter confirming her participation.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a previous update, I said this could be the biggest challenge of my career.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now sure it is.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last week I did some serious TT intervals to test my shape.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9881866222729415, \"rank\": 0.01195460186542106, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was surprised by the result, but there is still some work to do.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very happy though to announce that I made it to Paris!\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.413779637210084e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will see what will happen from here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Dijk will take on the ITT where, as a three-time World Champion in the discipline, she will be one of the favourites alongside current rainbow jersey holder Chloe Dygert (USA).\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.648845880816735e-32, \"text\": \"ITT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"rainbow jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\"}, {\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\", \"score\": 0.9999999166202577, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chloe Dygert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, fellow time trial specialistMarlen Reusser (Switzerland)announced earlier this week that she will not take the start due to a lingering illness.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will also make up part of a star-studded road race lineup alongsideDemi Vollering,Lorena Wiebes and Marianne Vos, withWiebes - the top sprinter in the world - set to be leader.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorena Wiebes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorena_Wiebes\"}, {\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marianne Vos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really looking forward to joining the team and showing something beautiful together in Paris,\\\" said Van Dijk in a KNWU press release, who also detailed just what it took to get to fitness on her social media.\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.413779637210084e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2283, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.033135118183959e-34, \"text\": \"KNWU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After surgery, I had to peddle with a cast first.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had to find a way to get on the bike.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Benjamin made all kinds of pedals so I could train with the cast,\\\" Van Dijk said.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2471, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.9649878114514775, \"rank\": 0.03628241947959187, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the cast was removed, I started to 'train' a little bit on the indoor trainer.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From 20-30 minutes with the cast to 2*75 minutes without the cast.\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I celebrated every step of the progression and I guess I was lucky that every time I tried something new, something extra, the ankle was ok with it.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not have done it without the help of [partner and son] Benjamin, Faas (although he has no clue), KNWU, Lidl-Trek and the incredible doctors of UMC Amsterdam.\\\"\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3013, \"end\": 3022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.200303987674334e-11, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Ellen van Dijk (@emvandijk)  A photo posted by on  James Moultrie is a gold-standard NCTJ journalist who joined\\u00a0Cyclingnews\\u00a0as a News Writer in 2023 after originally contributing as a freelancer for eight months, during which time he also wrote for Eurosport, Rouleur and Cycling Weekly.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3043, \"end\": 3057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_van_Dijk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen van Dijk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_van_Dijk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_van_Dijk\"}, {\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9382240025154192, \"rank\": 0.06583292831367749, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"score\": 0.9998843314627865, \"rank\": 0.00011568191666949279, \"text\": \"Moultrie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\"}, {\"begin\": 3128, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Council_for_the_Training_of_Journalists\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NCTJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Council_for_the_Training_of_Journalists\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Council_for_the_Training_of_Journalists\"}, {\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}, {\"begin\": 3303, \"end\": 3310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouleur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.330703631962582e-28, \"text\": \"Rouleur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouleur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouleur\"}, {\"begin\": 3315, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_Weekly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cycling Weekly\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_Weekly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_Weekly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to joining the team he reported on races such as Paris-Roubaix and the Giro d'Italia Donne for Eurosport and has interviewed some of the sport's top riders in Chlo\\u00e9 Dygert, Lizzie Deignan and Wout van Aert.\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 3496, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\", \"score\": 0.999